Description








                        
	
	
    
    
	
			Surround yourself in soft sophistication with this cotton sateen comforter set from Scott Living. The matching comforter, shams, and decorative pillows are an effortlessly elegant way to create the bedroom of your dreams. From Scott Living.
	    
  Includes one comforter, two shams, two decorative square pillows, and one decorative rectangular pillowKing sized: Comforter 104" x 96"; King shams 20" x 36"; Square pillows 16" x 16"; Rectangular pillow 12" x 20"100% cotton sateen, 300 thread count; fill 100% polyesterComforter/shams: machine wash, tumble dryDecorative pillows: spot clean onlyImported 









About Scott Living












