Coretta Scott King Civil Rights Activist 
Did you know that just four days after Martin Luther King Jr. died, Coretta Scott King led a march of 50,000 people to honor her husband? Coretta Scott King has worked tirelessly to gain civil rights for people around the world. Her story is sure to inspire and awe young readers.

















